Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.28,1:42:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughter]\NAnd you know who I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.80,1:42:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,People can be uh genuine to their own\Nbelief systems except their own belief
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.11,1:42:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,systems are delusional. That's the only\Nproblem. [laughter]
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.08,1:42:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So, we'll stop now and all\Nthe that want to uh after uh a break,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.92,1:42:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll answer more questions. We'll meet\Npeople personally, maybe answer some of
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.15,1:43:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,their personal questions.\NAnd no blissing out while on duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.80,1:43:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We just thought we'd ask answer some\Nmore questions.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.48,1:43:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Something something came up about the\Nlower astral.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.08,1:43:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, everything I've learned about it is\Nyou don't want to go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.11,1:43:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Let me ask that question. Somebody asked\Nthe question, can you evolve upwards
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.76,1:43:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,from the lower astral? We have\Npermission to ask this in front of this
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.88,1:43:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,audience. Resist.\N[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.40,1:43:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Do you have the karmic permission to to\Nto evolve from the lower astral? Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.08,1:43:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you don't want to go there.\NRemember the Buddhist said, "Fortunate
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.32,1:43:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,are you that you're a human being." Slim\Nare the chances to be born a human
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.96,1:43:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because the human has the chance to\Nevolve all the way to enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.60,1:44:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarer still is the desire to reach\Nenlightenment. And rarer still are those
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.60,1:44:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,who have heard of enlightenment, be born\Na human, and have not taken advantage of
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.28,1:44:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,this golden opportunity. Therefore,\Nwaste no time.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.67,1:44:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Waste no time.\NYou can waste no time very simply
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.08,1:44:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,because as everything arises in the\Nordinary course of ordinary life, you
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.04,1:44:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,just constantly surrender to God. You\Nknow, you don't have to be a rocket
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.71,1:44:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,scientist to figure out how to do that.\NYou know, could I would I be willing to
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.80,1:44:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender that to God? Those of you who\Nhave done the 12step programs, the third
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.56,1:44:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,step is you surrender your life to God\Nas you understand him. And of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.11,1:44:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the miracles all all the really basic\Nspiritual programs, many of which
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.71,1:44:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate in two or 300s, but they're ba\Nthey're solid basic stuff to surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.04,1:44:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,everything to God, to hold back nothing.\Num to ask God questions if you don't
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.96,1:45:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,know the answer to ask for guidance from\Nyour own from the Holy Spirit within
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.00,1:45:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you. Ask for a miracle\Nand uh you can often just tell the Holy
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.44,1:45:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit I don't get it and just and all\Nof a sudden you say I don't get it as
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.71,1:45:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you walk out suddenly you get it. I mean\N[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.56,1:45:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,very prompt I don't know you get very\Nprompt answers a lot of times.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.19,1:45:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Um\Nis there an ultimately best process for
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.92,1:45:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,releasing surrendering etc everything to\NGod that's the willingness we said the
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.56,1:45:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,power of willingness\Nsee devotion love takes many forms one
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.04,1:45:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,form it takes is is a powerful decision\Nwhen you make a decision to say no to
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.15,1:45:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is non-integrous\Nthat's really a very powerful step
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.15,1:45:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,uh I'm not going to go there and\Nwhatever the consequences. I'm not going
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.32,1:45:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,there. Um, so commitment, the\Nwillingness to um, let everything go. It
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.11,1:46:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean you're going to succeed the\Nfirst time you let go of a certain
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.76,1:46:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,desire or wantingness or resentment.\NDoesn't mean necessarily the first time
Dialogue: 0,1:46:07.36,1:46:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you let it go. We said because a lot of\Nthese things are an accumulation of of
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.15,1:46:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,many lifetimes and we'll get to that\Nnext week. a repetitive
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.11,1:46:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,uh pattern shows up over long expanses\Nof time. You know this is just one uh
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.56,1:46:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,episode. Uh one's life is not this\Nepisode. This is just an episode. This
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.88,1:46:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is this particular physicality. One's\Nlife transcends
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.36,1:46:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,uh many physicalities. So a pattern can\Npersist and persist and persist. So as
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.63,1:46:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you let go,\Ntry to let go of it, it doesn't always
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.56,1:46:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,let go right away. But the very fact\Nthat you were willing to surrender it
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.28,1:46:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and that you did actually go through the\Nprocess is already a karmic merit so
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.11,1:46:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that eventually you're building up you\Nmight say undoing all the negative
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.96,1:46:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,karmas and de and now all of a sudden\None day you you let it go and it
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.44,1:47:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,disappears.\NI don't know they just don't get you mad
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.56,1:47:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,anymore. You used to fantasize killing\Nthem and murdering them and getting
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.23,1:47:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,eaten with them and now you don't give a\Nrap about them one way or the other like
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.71,1:47:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,little mice. You know mice run around.\NAnd I think they're cute. You know, at
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.88,1:47:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,one time I'm sure I hated them, was\Nafraid of them, and uh you know, but I
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.76,1:47:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,now I think they're sort of cute. So I\Nchased them out. I hate to kill them
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.11,1:47:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because then I'll miss them and they're\Ngoing to go off in another body
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.67,1:47:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,elsewhere, but not in my backyard where\NI can have fun with them. So
Dialogue: 0,1:47:33.11,1:47:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,uh can you elaborate calibrations beyond\N10,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.80,1:47:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh such calibrations are possible. We\Ndon't want to really go into this. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.96,1:47:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Such calibrations are not\Npossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.63,1:47:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> We have permission.\N>> We have permission. We just to answer
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.44,1:47:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the question. It's possible for the\Nphysical nervous system to handle
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.52,1:47:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,everything something over a thousand. It\Nit's possible for the human nervous
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.08,1:48:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,system\Nto handle consciousness energies over
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.08,1:48:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,1,000. No. Says no.\NUh,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.11,1:48:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody said if you if this last time\Nyou came out of the void, did you leave
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.48,1:48:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the last you left the last time in the\Nvoid? Resist. We have permission on that
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.04,1:48:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,one. The prior lifetime was left in the\Nvoid. Resist. Yes. For prior lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.96,1:48:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in fact, the the ultimate truth was\Nvoidness as far as I knew. And uh
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.28,1:48:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a certain\Nspiritual pathway which is integrous
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.56,1:48:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's based on a conviction that\Nthat is the ultimate truth and it's
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.36,1:48:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,based on a mistransation I think of the\Nteaching of the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.56,1:48:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Um\Nbecause it is only really a matter of
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.28,1:49:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,contextualization.\NThe difference between allness and
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.40,1:49:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,nothingness is a very subtle discernment\Non a certain level that which is all
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.84,1:49:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,thereby becomes nothing. You understand?\NBecause to be something you would have
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.15,1:49:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to be differentiated from the rest. So\Nto be all that is is in a way being
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.60,1:49:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing but it is more complicated than\Nthat u verbalization about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.19,1:49:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So this the capacity to let things go is\Nfirst of all a matter of practice, a
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.28,1:49:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,matter of direction, a p a matter of\Nhabit, a matter a matter of willingness
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.36,1:49:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and basically it's really devotional.\NSo the underpinning of any spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.84,1:49:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,practice is devotion.\NUm the willingness to surrender all to
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.67,1:49:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,God.\NUm and that's what gives us its its
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.71,1:50:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,power.\NWith practice it becomes uh habit. With
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.60,1:50:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,practice it becomes habitual.\NUh you let go to change it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.40,1:50:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking out back about being\Nstopped by a cop at 1:00 in the morning
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.48,1:50:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,on 89A.\NYeah. We were the only ones on the whole
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.71,1:50:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,highway. Nobody's out there at 1:00\Nexcept me and this squad car behind me.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.67,1:50:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I figure I'm looking at my\Nspeedometer. I'm thinking I'm going 40.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.52,1:50:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, why is this guy telling me? So,\Nfinally pulls me over, flashes, lights,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.23,1:50:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said, "Uh, what can it be?" He\Nsays, "You're weaving?"
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.00,1:50:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Weaving? What is weaving? He said,\N"You're going back and forth over the
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.32,1:50:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,yellow line." I'm thinking, "We're the\Nonly people on the whole highway. What
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.96,1:50:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,am I going to do? Stay in my lane?\NThere's nobody else here but me."
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.36,1:50:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughter]\NSo, he says, "Are are you drinking?" I
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.56,1:50:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,said, "No, I haven't had a drink in 40\Nyears." So he says, "Uh, you take dope,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.15,1:51:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,smoke stuff?" I said, "No."\N[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.08,1:51:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"You willing to take a so and so test?"\NI says, "Sure." He says, "Walk this
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.88,1:51:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,yellow line." I walk the yellow line. He\Nsaid, "I don't know. There's still
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.84,1:51:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,something wrong with you." [laughter]\NAnd he's scratching his head. He said,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.92,1:51:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Well, what do you think's the matter\Nwith you?" All right. And I said, "You
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.76,1:51:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,know, you want me to be truthful?" He\Nsays, "Yeah." I said, "I don't feel like
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.84,1:51:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really in my body."\N[cheering]
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.76,1:51:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, "Good God." He says, "I've had\Nthis exactly the same experience."
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.52,1:51:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it was a an actual experience. said,\Nyou know, I'm stringing this to God and
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.76,1:51:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,uh you know, if he gives me a ticket, he\Ngives me a ticket, so let it be. You
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.59,1:51:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,know, he said, gosh, he said, I'm glad\Nto have met you. And then I told him,
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.04,1:52:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a doctor and a psychiatrist and all\Nthat gave really more firepower. And I
Dialogue: 0,1:52:01.76,1:52:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,told him, yeah, I go out by if I don't\Nremember to come back in it, I can
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.52,1:52:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,wander off because, you know, if you're\Nwandering across in the middle of the
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.88,1:52:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,night, you're not thinking about what\Nyou're doing, you know. So anyway, he
Dialogue: 0,1:52:11.84,1:52:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,was greatly relieved. He said, "This\Nworried me for years." He said, "Now I
Dialogue: 0,1:52:14.80,1:52:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,know what it is." I said, "You just will\Nyourself to be back in the body." And
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.63,1:52:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,bang, you go back. Terrific. You know,\Nwe left the best buddies, shook hands,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.44,1:52:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,hugged.\NSo, one sign of being out of your body
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.71,1:52:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is you weave.\N[laughter]
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.28,1:52:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was really a nice officer. You\Nknow, he really was. He said, "I really
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.67,1:52:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,had been worried about that." And here\Nhe found somebody he could ask about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.71,1:52:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, you know, you're not just\Nnot connected with your body space,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.71,1:52:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,which is one problem that you have when\Nyou're first going into certain higher
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.32,1:52:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,states. You don't know where your body\Nis in space. It was it's very difficult
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.84,1:53:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to navigate because that which is the\Ncentral controller is gone. See,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.96,1:53:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,everything you do is oriented from some\Nimaginary space somewhere in the middle
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.71,1:53:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of your head. When that disappears,\Nwhere you are in space is not all that
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.96,1:53:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,clear at all. It's still not all that\Nclear very often.
